The 2020 Maxda CX-5 is the most powerful CX-5 ever. Poised under pressure, the CX-5 Grand Touring Reserve and Signature feature a powerful and efficient  -G 2.5T engine that gives you power to pursue your passions. It also features an innovative dynamic pressure turbocharger that responds instantaneously, nearly eliminating turbo lag. The CX-5’s Signature model adds numerous premium touches to the thoughtfully designed interior. Genuine layered wood trim, Caturra Brown Nappa leather seats and ambient cabin lighting, to name just a few, combine to indulge the senses of both driver and passenger. With the CX-5, safety is second nature and first priority. The suite of standard i-Activsense safety features ingenious technologies that can help alert you to potential hazards. Features like Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and Lane Departure Warning System can help you avoid collisions—or lessen their impact. You want to be focused and engaged when you drive, and that starts with feeling confident behind the wheel. Weather and road conditions can change in an instant so available i-Activ AWD helps predict when all-wheel drive might be needed by monitoring factors like outside temperature, throttle input, steering and braking patterns and even windshield wiper usage. It can then preemptively optimize power to the wheels, helping maintain traction. All this happens without you even feeling a change. And that’s the idea.
